_Ok trying to remember all these names is hard, it's thanksgiving, time to enlist some help_. If you would like to have your name added to the veteran list please post in this thread to prove you are indeed still here and are not just a spirit. If you have other additions to the other tiers please inform me of who I am missing so I can add them to the appropriate tier.

Happy Thanksgiving everyone!

(I have a feeling I'll be updating this as time permits today, but I will get to it in pieces.)
